long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Spear Throwing is a fun shooting game where you and a tribe member throw spears by paying attention to the area we come across.

There is a tribe member in the game. With this tribe member, we accelerate by running in a field and throwing spears before reaching the line. By adjusting the direction of the Spear well, we throw it as far as possible and get points. We continue the game by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Throwing the Spear is a fun shooting game designed with us in mind for skill game lovers.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Spear Throwing Game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
